                    <p>There is no author rebuttal period for the demo track. The review committee will render acceptance decisions directly based on reviews and committee discussion.</p>
                    <p>Demo submissions are <strong>single-blind</strong>: author names and affiliations are visible to you. This is intentional. For demos, knowing the team and context behind a system helps you evaluate feasibility and production readiness. Do not hold author identity against them or in their favor.</p>
                    <p class="mb-0">If you are unable to complete your reviews on time, or if you receive a demo entirely outside your expertise, contact the demo chairs as early as possible. Late notification is far more disruptive than early notification.</p>
                </section>

